Dialogs.Dialog: I feel like there aren't many emails lately. Are you avoiding me?
...... Maybe we are in a state of malaise?
Is that so with me? However, I haven't received much email recently.
Is that so. I can't help it anymore.
you know what. I feel that the number of emails is decreasing...
I'm waiting every day. If you don't email me more...
It looks like it's already shining...
About me... You're not bored, right?
sorry. Somehow... I feel like the number of kisses has decreased.
……I do not think so. Not kissing doesn't mean you don't like it.
Hey, don't you want to get cold lately?
Well, I don't think that's the case...
But recently he hasn't kissed me so much.
Or do you have any complaints about me?
Hey, are you aware? What we are lacking these days.
Don't let me say this much...
You've broken your date promise several times. why?
Meet me... I don't hate it.
(I'm a little in a bad mood...)
Is that so? Is it because of ●?
Why don't you just go out on a date many times and don't think about it?
Do you reflect on it properly? Hmm?
Hey, I have a story, is that okay?
Around this time, you didn't keep your promise properly. I'm looking forward to every date.
I don't want to say this if possible. You know.
(I have to make sure I don't get angry anymore)
Hey, I want to talk a little.
I've been on a date the other day....... What happened?
...... Don't do it anymore. I'll be sad.
(It looks like you're in a bad mood, that's right)
Last date. I was silent all the time.
What's up. Keep girlfriends on the date all the time.
Please reflect on how I felt.
Are you okay I... I want to meet more.
Hey, how can I meet more?
(It seems to make me feel a little lonely...)
What do you think of us these days?
What do you think... what do you mean?
I don't think I can meet you so much.
I want to see more if possible... I think so.
Well... I want to see you more.
You're meeting like this right now, right?
That's right... I haven't seen him recently.
I'm so lonely. I want to meet more and more...
Well, I'm just an ordinary friend. I am curious?
Just a bit. But it's just a little. I don't care.
(It seems that you care a little...)
You're very close to the person you just mentioned.
I do not think so? Although it was an ordinary friend.
Yeah... I wonder if I care too much?
Who is the girl now? It seemed to be good friends.
I'm just a friend... ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, are you jealous?
It's not like that... I don't care.
Is it going to get rid of your cold?
Because that cold, wasn't it from ●?
Hmm... I don't know. Don't worry about that.
I don't look like that. If you rest properly, you will be cured.
Maybe so. But you don't have to worry about that.
I'm fine... I'll be cured as soon as I rest.
sorry. Did you get that cold from ●?
do not apologize. I don't think it's your fault.
I want to take responsibility. The cold, ● will bring it home.
I'm dressing up... That word is enough.
Return the cold. Then will you be fine?
Already. There is no end, if that happens.
● Please give it a try. ● Because of that, ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ is...
...... Rejected. I don't want you to suffer. I just need to cure it properly.
I don't apologize... but I'm happy.
It ’s good. Instead, play a lot when you're fine, right?
Don't look so cute. Your sister's fever will rise, right?
Oh yeah, I cut the apples. Can you eat
Okay, okay. Make it a comfortable posture.
Thank you for your kindness today. Thanks to that, it seems to be cured soon.
Yup. Then ● is about to go home. I'll be fine, I'm waiting.
Already completely. Sorry to worry you.
I'm glad... but I couldn't go to see you.
okay. I didn't have to transfer it to you. Right.
(Until I'm worried about ●... I should have visited you)
Did you get rid of your cold?
I managed to do it myself because you wouldn't come to visit me.
Ah... I'm sorry I can't go.
joke. I don't want to show you where I'm weak.
(But after all, he was happy when I went...)
Are you okay with a cold?
I'm glad... I was thinking of going to see you, but I was cured before that.
Oh, that's a shame. I wanted you to take care of me.
▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, are you feeling well anymore?
I'm glad... I think I'm fine.
It's a sympathy effect. Were you okay after that?
Oh no problem. Tell me when you have a cold again.
Do you kiss every time you get a cold? It might be good too.
I'm glad, it looks like I'm fine.
I don't say that straight anymore.
Hey, isn't it painful to talk to me? All right?
All right. Rather, he's getting better.
Your cold... Can I try to get rid of it?
Are you feeling sick? You have to sleep properly.
I'm not a child, so I'm sleeping quietly.
I have a cold, it looks tight. Should I take it home or give it a try?
Thank you. Don't get sick until ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
Hey... Isn't it possible to get rid of a cold by kissing it? Try out?
Yeah... I'll give it a try.
I intended to be a joke, but... then, why don't you try it?
You have to try it to see if it's true?
Oh. I feel like I'm getting stronger.
Was good. Then I got a cold.
Yeah... I got a lot of energy.
Was good. Then, if I catch a cold with this, take care of me like I do now, right?
You can't move it. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ collapses.
What are you saying? If you don't move, you won't heal.
Get rid of your cold quickly. Please.
I know. You can't date unless both of you are fine.
Yes, thank you. I feel that my body has become lighter.
Me too. Did the cold go somewhere?
Not so... I suddenly got shy.
That's not good. ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲ will catch a cold, right?
I'm fine with that... Yeah, I see.
That's impossible. It won't heal even if you move.
Hmm... I think that's what it is.
Are you hungry? I made porridge...
You can eat it. Let's eat!
Thank you for your sympathy and I'm fine!
Was good. Then I should excuse myself. Please rest properly until it is completely healed.
Are you overdoing it? Is it really healed?
As you can see, it's pin-pinned.
It's not such an exaggeration. thanks for worrying about me.
Congratulations on your return. It's all right now?
Oh. Originally it wasn't such a bad cold.
Well, if you're so fine, you don't have to spoil it.
I'm glad I was cured... I was worried.
Thank you. Because there is nothing anymore.
Even if I couldn't meet you, I'll spoil you.
I got rid of my cold. Thanks to ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲.
I wonder if it was worth going to visit.
By the way... is that okay? I have a cold...
I? It's okay, it looks like it didn't move.
I finally got rid of my cold.
Yeah, that's good. Is it my sympathy effect?
Oh yeah, thank you for that time. …… After that, what about ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲?
Ah, uh... this one was fine too.
Thanks to ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, my cold has healed properly.
Was good. The kiss at that time worked.
That's right... that means it's moving over there...
All right. I didn't get a cold either.
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, maybe a little different from usual?)
You might be surprised if you say this...
What... Of course, about you. No good?
It's not bad, but... I'm not surprised, it's natural.
It's natural, but... it's not natural. Because...
I like it so much... different from usual.
I'm sorry, you're saying something strange... I'm a little strange...
I like it so much that it goes crazy...
...... It's decided. Love love. I love you!
The face is hot... it seems to explode...
No... I don't want to hear it. When I hear it, it really explodes...
(Such a bold ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲…… More than usual ……)
If you ban it, ban it!
(▲姉ヶ崎＊▲, something much more than usual...)
